This folder contains code files (python) related to the Assignment-1 of CS6690 pattern recognition.

source files:
----------------------------
There are 2 main files & 1 helper file (library) as mentioned below.

pr_helper.py  : A python module which contains reusable APIs for image_processing.py, linear_regression.py modules
linear_regression.py : Python module which takes input as the datasets for linear regression & fits polynomial models to the data
image_processing.py: Python module to decompose the image (SVD, EVD) and analyse the properties

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Prerequisites:
----------------------------
Python 2.7.6
sudo apt-get install numpy
sudo apt-get install scipy
sudo apt-get install opencv2
